          "label": "a",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "With guidance from your counselor, establish a four-week training plan that combines your chosen multisport format to develop proper techniques, gain self-confidence, and increase endurance. Each session should last at least 25 minutes and include a proper warmup before the session and stretching afterward."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [
            {
              "title": "Advice for Younger Athletes | Our Trips for Junior and Youth Triathletes (video)",
